{"tid":1928157,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"光復正體中文字","createTime":"2020-03-16T08:27:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T12:03:54.000Z","uid":220740,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"34b2a0b277fb1066abe9a30e929d5eac90a7618e","tid":1928157,"uid":220740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T08:27:35.000Z","msg":"眼見依家唔少香港人因為貪快而用殘體字，咁樣落去，正體字好快就會失傳，所以想出翻個post呼籲香港人用翻繁體字，唔好令繁體字文化失傳！<br />\n<br />\n以下有啲喺「香港中文監察」fb page搵，另外大部分係自己google同自己諗，有錯歡迎指出/提出更多缺少咗意思既殘體字例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋我會用書面語去解釋，希望可以等更多識中文既人明。<br />\n<br />\n產➡️产：不能<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">生</span></span>，怎樣產？<br />\n<br />\n麵➡️面：無<span style=\"color: red;\">麥</span>，怎樣做麵，還是做假的面？<br />\n<br />\n飛➡️<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">飞</span></span>：單翼又升不起，怎樣飛？<br />\n<br />\n湧➡️涌：沒有<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">力</span></span>，想湧又能怎樣？<br />\n<br />\n廠➡️<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">厂</span></span>：廠都空空了。<br />\n<br />\n協➡️协：排擠他力，怎能協？<br />\n<br />\n導➡️导：領導者，已無<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">道</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n親➡️亲：不能相<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">見</span></span>，怎能相親？<br />\n<br />\n愛➡️爱：愛無<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">心</span></span>，怎樣愛？<br />\n<br />\n雲➡️云：雲無雨，怎能稱得上做雲？<br />\n<br />\n買➡️买：無貝（古代的錢），怎樣買？<br />\n<br />\n災➡️灾：災，火燒了，上頭冒煙了，這是正常現象；灾，火燒了，上頭蓋起來，這是他們的特色。<br />\n<br />\n國➡️国：國無<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">口</span></span>，又怎能發表自己的言論，然而這亦是他們的特色。<br />\n<br />\n義➡️义：不講道義，因為不關<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我</span></span>事。<br />\n<br />\n鄉➡️乡：回望故鄉，已不見<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">郎</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n進➡️进：不是越來越佳，而是往井裏走，又怎能進步呢？<br />\n<br />\n辦➡️办：沒有<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">力</span></span>，怎樣辦事？<br />\n<br />\n選➡️选：如何選擇，不得<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">共</span></span>同決定，而是部份人優<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">先</span></span><br />\n<br />\n誌➡️志：報紙雜誌，有苦情而不能<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">言</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n開➡️开：開關無<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">門</span></span><br />\n<br />\n窮➡️穷：窮人是否不再弓身，而獲得了力量？<br />\n<br />\n聽➡️听：沒有<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">耳</span></span>，又怎能聽？<br />\n<br />\n日曆➡️历：沒有<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">日</span></span>子，又何謂日曆？<br />\n<br />\n兒➡️儿：兒沒首。"},{"pid":"c141b08615cbb4da2b4dee3cbfb1f3e448803231","tid":1928157,"uid":319824,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T08:29:04.000Z","msg":"唔識寫/打殘體"},{"pid":"1fb06d2b37bb238e232bfc68b4b85055f83b1f9f","tid":1928157,"uid":105843,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T08:30:16.000Z","msg":"唔小心禁左負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"010817b83693cf8dbe0950f850dc7a3e0f130a67","tid":1928157,"uid":220740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c141b08615cbb4da2b4dee3cbfb1f3e448803231","tid":1928157,"uid":319824,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T08:29:04.000Z","msg":"唔識寫/打殘體"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T08:31:07.000Z","msg":"咁係好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都唔識，我好多字都係就咁打左先，再用iphone個繁變簡功能變簡體"},{"pid":"699107dedfee7429670c1b138a23fa5ac9f78b2c","tid":1928157,"uid":174432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T08:32:36.000Z","msg":"5p字同理"},{"pid":"55294e06a4ca45b1e71380872db6d53bc16abe2a","tid":1928157,"uid":202412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T08:34:18.000Z","msg":"啲字真係殘架 全部斷手斷腳 甩皮甩骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/so